 \bar{X}_n = \frac{1}{n} \sum_{i=1}^n X_i  
 E(\bar{X}_n) = E(\frac{1}{n} \sum_{i=1}^n X_i)  
 = \frac{1}{n} \sum_{i=1}^n E(X_i) = \frac{1}{n}n\mu 
 = \mu 
